Class DeletedCertificate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.azure.security.keyvault.certificates.models.CertificateBase
      • com.azure.security.keyvault.certificates.models.DeletedCertificate

  • public final class DeletedCertificate
extends CertificateBase
    Deleted Certificate is the resource consisting of name, recovery id, deleted date, scheduled purge date and its attributes inherited from CertificateBase. It is managed by Secret Service.
